2023 has been an incredible year for me as I entered into the world of mobile game development. When I initially started, I had my doubts about whether I could truly make it happen, but with the support of my besties, I achieved it! 💛

I was pleasantly surprised by the overwhelming love our games received. My inbox has been flooded with messages expressing the appreciation for the games, and I've also received numerous requests for updates, which, admittedly, added a bit of pressure 😅

Unfortunately, unexpected changes led to a delay in the launch of our donut truck game. However, I'm thrilled to announce that it will be available to the public in December. I really really appreciate all of your patience! 🥹

Magic Escape is my first puzzle game and also my first paid game, representing a bold trial. I enjoyed designing these little puzzles, weaving a magical world, and presenting it to all of you. Although this game hasn't been able to generate many downloads (might because it is a paid game), I take pride in this trial myself! ✨

Lastly, I want to let you know that we have an exciting game coming in February 2024 — Resolving Sushi🍣! This is the game that I've spent the longest time designing and developing. You'll have the opportunity to run a sushi restaurant alongside the most adorable doggie friends. The best part? It's available for free download!

I want to emphasize that this is just the beginning of our journey together. I'm committed to bringing you even more enjoyable games in 2024. I am sincerely grateful for all the support! Thank you for being a part of this incredible journey!💛
